      "The humidifier is suitable for living rooms, children‚Äôs and workspaces, helping to avoid issues caused by dry air, which can cause discomfort and negatively affect health.",
    Humidifier_Xiaomi_5_text_2:
      "It also features a low noise level, allowing use even at night without disturbing sleep quality. The Smartmi Evaporative Humidifier 3 Lite effectively purifies water, providing quality humidified air without harming your health.",
    Humidifier_Xiaomi_4_text:
      "The Xiaomi Smartmi Evaporative Humidifier 3 Lite 4L EU (CJXJSQ06ZM) White is an evaporative air humidifier with an evaporation rate of 280 ml/h and a reservoir capacity of 4 liters. The humidifier can work continuously for up to 14 hours, with a noise level of just 50 dB. The device supports adjustment of evaporation intensity and three operating modes: automatic, night, and humidity maintenance. The air humidifier is user-friendly: it can be placed on the floor or on a table; water is filled from the top. The service area is 40 m¬≤.",
