      "With an airflow rate of 510 m¬≥/h, it is suitable for operation in rooms up to 60 m¬≤. The carbon and pre-filter trap large dust particles and odors. HEPA H13 locks in pollen, spores and similar allergens. The electrostatic filter removes ultrafine dust, soot and smoke from the air. The catalytic UV cartridge eliminates bacteria and viruses. Relevant indicators alert you when filter replacement is needed.",
