      "A night mode is provided in the purifier, during which the device is almost silent and the panel lights are dimmed. In the smartphone app, you can set the night mode to automatically switch on in the evening and off in the morning. The purifier‚Äôs display shows the current PM2.5 (¬µg/m¬≥) concentration.",
